# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Vivado / Vitis generated files
# Keep source RTL, XDC, Tcl, and intentional project files.
# Ignore tool-generated outputs and run products.
# ------------------------------------------------------------
**/.Xil/
**/*.cache/
**/*.gen/
**/*.runs/
**/*.sim/
**/*.hw/
**/*.ip_user_files/

*.jou
*.log
*.str
*.pb

